summary: This document is a chain of emails from November 2021 regarding the coordination and transmission of a proffer agreement and an associated FBI 302 interview report. The correspondence involves members of the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force and an Assistant United States Attorney from the Southern District of New York.

keyFacts: The document is an email chain from November 2021 concerning a proffer agreement and an FBI 302 interview report.
The correspondence involves the NYPD/FBI Child Exploitation Human Trafficking Task Force and an Assistant United States Attorney.
A proffer agreement is being prepared and sent to an individual identified as 'EL' for initialing.
An FBI 302 interview report is referenced and attached, indicating an interview related to the investigation.
The document shows ongoing investigative and legal coordination in late 2021 regarding the Epstein case.
